# Object Property: obo:APOLLO_SV_00000037 (commissions)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000037 "a commissions b, iff a does not participate in the creation or execution of b and participates in a legal agreement that c participates on the creation or execution of b and c getting something in exchange for that participation."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000600 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000037 "A relation between two entities where the first entity formally requests a third party to create or execute the second entity."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(apollo_sv:APOLLO_SV_0000040 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000037 "commissions")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label obo:APOLLO_SV_00000037 "commissions"@en)
