AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 obo:RO_0002212 "Chris Mungall"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 obo:RO_0002212 <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ro/docs/causal-relations>)
