# Class: obo:APOLLO_SV_00000092 (95% confidence interval)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000600 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000092 "a type of interval estimate of a population parameter used to indicate the reliability of an estimate.  How frequently the observed interval contains the parameter is determined by the confidence level or confidence coefficient, in this type the confidence level is 95%"@en)
