AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000600 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000093 "a type of interval estimate of a population parameter that has the property that the true value of the estimated populatin parameter has a (specified) particular probability of being in the confidence interval given the data on which the estimate is derived."@en)
