AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000195 "An organism population that is the target for a disease control strategy."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000600 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000195 "An organism population that is the target for a disease control strategy."@en)
