# Class: obo:APOLLO_SV_00000256 (Weibull Distribution)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000256 "A continuous parametric probability distribution that gives the distribution of lifetimes of objects. It was originally proposed to quantify fatigue data, but it is also used in analysis of systems involving a \"weakest link.\""@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000256 "Mathias Brochhausen"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000600 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000256 "A continuous parametric probability distribution that gives the distribution of lifetimes of objects. It was originally proposed to quantify fatigue data, but it is also used in analysis of systems involving a \"weakest link.\""@en)
