# Class: obo:APOLLO_SV_00000308 (vector control strategy)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000308 "An infectious disease control strategy that has a vector control action specification as part."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000308 "William R. Hogan"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000600 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000308 "An infectious disease control strategy that attempts to reduce infections in a population of a particular host species by limiting infection acquisitions from a second host species, called the 'vector'."@en)
