AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000323 "An infectious disease conrol straegy that seeks to reduce disease transmission by offering employees extra paid time off to stay home, in an attempt to reduce contacts that transmit disease in the workplace."@en)
