AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000334 "An infection acquisition by which a pathogen organism from a particular biological taxon, which previously was participating in a colonization process in a host organism from another taxon, begins to invade the tissues of the same host organism and reproduce there."@en)
