# Class: obo:APOLLO_SV_00000370 (deprecated homeostasis)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000370 "A disposition of the whole organism (or of some causally relatively isolated part of the organism, such as a single cell) to regulate its bodily processes in such a way as (1) to maintain bodily qualities within a certain range or profile and (2) to respond successfully to departures from this range caused by internal influences or environmental influences such as poisoning."@en)
