AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000463 "A conditional specification for some epidemic simulator that is triggered by a Boolean value that, if true, specifies that there is a non-uniform distribution of oviposition site carrying capacities in a simulated vector population."@en)
