AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000468 "William R. Hogan")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000600 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000468 "An epidemic simulator action specification that, when set to true, results in the simulator clearing each simulated artificially-infected vector of its simulated infection whenever it migrates out of the simulated population location."@en)
