AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment obo:APOLLO_SV_00000511 "Note that infections that are acquired in this manner do not fall within the class of sexually transmitted infections (STI's), ipso facto. This type of transmission can also occur with non-STI pathogens--such as meningitis and Zika."@en)
