AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000600 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000622 "A count of cases from the beginning of the epidemic until recently."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment obo:APOLLO_SV_00000622 "The count is also nearly always geographically localized, for example, the case count for the state of Pennsylvania or the case count for Waukesha County, Wisconsin."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label obo:APOLLO_SV_00000622 "cumulative epidemic case count"@en)
