# Class: obo:APOLLO_SV_00000650 (intent to have a ward vaccinated)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000111 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000650 "guardian's intent to have a ward under their care vaccinated"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000650 "An intentionality inhering in a person bearing a guardian role and that is directed at their future participation in an authorization for the vaccination or other immunization of a person under their care and who bears a ward role."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000650 "William R. Hogan"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000600 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000650 "The intent of a guardian to have a ward under their care vaccinated in the near future."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment obo:APOLLO_SV_00000650 "Legally, this covers the situation of a parent intending to have their child vaccinated. That is because the parent(s) is(are) the natural gaurdian of the child. Other individuals appointed by a court as guardian are legal guardians. If the specific case of parent / child is required, we could create a subclass of this one where the guardian = parent of the ward, and ward = child. However, that could get into issues of adoption, etc.  At the current time we do not have guardian role and ward role classes in OMRSE."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label obo:APOLLO_SV_00000650 "intent to have a ward vaccinated"@en)
SubClassOf(obo:APOLLO_SV_00000650 obo:MF_0000073)

# Class: obo:APOLLO_SV_00000651 (reproduction)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000111 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000651 "organism reproduction"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000651 "The process by which new organisms are created from existing ones."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000651 "William R. Hogan"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(apollo_sv:APOLLO_SV_0000040 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000651 "Reproduction")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label obo:APOLLO_SV_00000651 "reproduction"@en)
EquivalentClasses(obo:APOLLO_SV_00000651 ObjectUnionOf(obo:GO_0019058 obo:GO_0019953 obo:GO_0019954))
SubClassOf(obo:APOLLO_SV_00000651 obo:GO_0008150)

# Class: obo:APOLLO_SV_00000652 (intent to have a child vaccinated)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000652 "An intent to have a ward vaccinated where the guardian is a parent (natural or adoptive) and the ward is a child (natural or adopted) of that parent, and the parent has not otherwise been legally barred from making healthcare decisions for the child."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000117 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000652 "William R. Hogan"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000600 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000652 "Intent to have one's child vaccinated."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment obo:APOLLO_SV_00000652 "The case of adult children is eliminated through the use of guardian and ward roles in the definition. The parent no longer has a guardian role, and the child no longer has a ward role, once the child is of legal age to make their own decisions. That is, those roles cease to exist."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label obo:APOLLO_SV_00000652 "intent to have a child vaccinated"@en)
SubClassOf(obo:APOLLO_SV_00000652 obo:APOLLO_SV_00000650)

